title: Luxury Studio w/ Private Terrace - Prospect Heights New Development
posting_body: ['Come experience the next level of luxury living in Prospect Heights - brand new development 51 story Brooklyn Crossing offered with world class amenities.', 'Call / Text Ko @ (929)-408-8354 for an appointment.', 'Quiet Studio home with Private Terrace and in home washer/dryer', 'Designed by Perkins Eastman, with amenities designed by Lemay + Escobar, Brooklyn Crossing offers 51 stories of custom-appointed residences and amenities to create the next chapter in your life story.', 'Studio and 1- to 3-bedroom apartments, with resident amenities designed for being still or being in the center of the action, whenever you choose.', 'Here, space abounds to stretch solo or spin with friends in the expansive fitness center, make it a movie night in the resident Screening Room, or people-watch on the open-air rooftop complete with a Sky Lounge, outdoor pool, and 360-degree views stretching from the Manhattan skyline to Rockaway Beach.', "Situated in prime Prospect Heights, you're minutes from epic culture and culinary fare in every direction, including historic landmarks like the Brooklyn Academy of Music and dynamic new destinations like Barclays Center.", 'Add to that 10 train lines one block away, and really, you can go anywhere you want from here.']
